comment:
* This class encapsulates information about an object on an MTP device.
 * This corresponds to the ObjectInfo Dataset described in
 * section 5.3.1 of the MTP specification.

methods.name: public final int getObjectHandle()
methods.comment:
* Returns the object handle for the MTP object
     *
     * @return the object handle

methods.name: public final int getStorageId()
methods.comment:
* Returns the storage ID for the MTP object's storage unit
     *
     * @return the storage ID

methods.name: public final int getFormat()
methods.comment:
* Returns the format code for the MTP object
     *
     * @return the format code

methods.name: public final int getProtectionStatus()
public final int getCompressedSize()
methods.comment:
* Returns the size of the MTP object
     *
     * @return the object size

methods.name: public final long getCompressedSizeLong()
methods.comment:
* Returns the size of the MTP object
     *
     * @return the object size

methods.name: public final int getThumbFormat()
methods.comment:
* Returns the format code for the MTP object's thumbnail
     * Will be zero for objects with no thumbnail
     *
     * @return the thumbnail format code

methods.name: public final int getThumbCompressedSize()
methods.comment:
* Returns the size of the MTP object's thumbnail
     * Will be zero for objects with no thumbnail
     *
     * @return the thumbnail size

methods.name: public final long getThumbCompressedSizeLong()
methods.comment:
* Returns the size of the MTP object's thumbnail
     * Will be zero for objects with no thumbnail
     *
     * @return the thumbnail size

methods.name: public final int getThumbPixWidth()
methods.comment:
* Returns the width of the MTP object's thumbnail in pixels
     * Will be zero for objects with no thumbnail
     *
     * @return the thumbnail width

methods.name: public final long getThumbPixWidthLong()
methods.comment:
* Returns the width of the MTP object's thumbnail in pixels
     * Will be zero for objects with no thumbnail
     *
     * @return the thumbnail width

methods.name: public final int getThumbPixHeight()
methods.comment:
* Returns the height of the MTP object's thumbnail in pixels
     * Will be zero for objects with no thumbnail
     *
     * @return the thumbnail height

methods.name: public final long getThumbPixHeightLong()
methods.comment:
* Returns the height of the MTP object's thumbnail in pixels
     * Will be zero for objects with no thumbnail
     *
     * @return the thumbnail height

methods.name: public final int getImagePixWidth()
methods.comment:
* Returns the width of the MTP object in pixels
     * Will be zero for non-image objects
     *
     * @return the image width

methods.name: public final long getImagePixWidthLong()
methods.comment:
* Returns the width of the MTP object in pixels
     * Will be zero for non-image objects
     *
     * @return the image width

methods.name: public final int getImagePixHeight()
methods.comment:
* Returns the height of the MTP object in pixels
     * Will be zero for non-image objects
     *
     * @return the image height

methods.name: public final long getImagePixHeightLong()
methods.comment:
* Returns the height of the MTP object in pixels
     * Will be zero for non-image objects
     *
     * @return the image height

methods.name: public final int getImagePixDepth()
methods.comment:
* Returns the depth of the MTP object in bits per pixel
     * Will be zero for non-image objects
     *
     * @return the image depth

methods.name: public final long getImagePixDepthLong()
methods.comment:
* Returns the depth of the MTP object in bits per pixel
     * Will be zero for non-image objects
     *
     * @return the image depth

methods.name: public final int getParent()
methods.comment:
* Returns the object handle for the object's parent
     * Will be zero for the root directory of a storage unit
     *
     * @return the object's parent

methods.name: public final int getAssociationType()
methods.comment:
* Returns the association type for the MTP object
     * Will be zero objects that are not of format
     * {@link android.mtp.MtpConstants#FORMAT_ASSOCIATION}
     * For directories the association type is typically
     * {@link android.mtp.MtpConstants#ASSOCIATION_TYPE_GENERIC_FOLDER}
     *
     * @return the object's association type

methods.name: public final int getAssociationDesc()
methods.comment:
* Returns the association description for the MTP object
     * Will be zero objects that are not of format
     * {@link android.mtp.MtpConstants#FORMAT_ASSOCIATION}
     *
     * @return the object's association description

methods.name: public final int getSequenceNumber()
methods.comment:
* Returns the sequence number for the MTP object
     * This field is typically not used for MTP devices,
     * but is sometimes used to define a sequence of photos
     * on PTP cameras.
     *
     * @return the object's sequence number

methods.name: public final long getSequenceNumberLong()
methods.comment:
* Returns the sequence number for the MTP object
     * This field is typically not used for MTP devices,
     * but is sometimes used to define a sequence of photos
     * on PTP cameras.
     *
     * @return the object's sequence number

methods.name: public final String getName()
methods.comment:
* Returns the name of the MTP object
     *
     * @return the object's name

methods.name: public final long getDateCreated()
methods.comment:
* Returns the creation date of the MTP object
     * The value is represented as milliseconds since January 1, 1970
     *
     * @return the object's creation date

methods.name: public final long getDateModified()
methods.comment:
* Returns the modification date of the MTP object
     * The value is represented as milliseconds since January 1, 1970
     *
     * @return the object's modification date

methods.name: public final String getKeywords()
methods.comment:
* Returns a comma separated list of keywords for the MTP object
     *
     * @return the object's keyword list

methods.name: private static int longToUint32(long value, String valueName)

methodNames: private static int longToUint32(long value, String valueName)
